title: Japanese firm Mitsui Sumitomo makes £3.47bn swoop for Amlin
text: Japanese firm Mitsui Sumitomo makes £3.47bn swoop for Amlin Mitsui Sumitomo announces huge bid for FTSE 250 insurer Amlin Amlin sponsors a team in the Formula E electric car championship, which raced in the streets of London in June 2015 Photo: Getty Images By Andrew Trotman , and Jon Yeomans 8:08AM BST 08 Sep 2015
